### Viewer UI

- [x] Add `subagent-tree-view.ts`.
- [x] Implement `openSubagentViewer(ctx)`.
- [x] Open viewer with `ctx.ui.custom()` in overlay mode.
- [x] Render tree selection mode.
- [x] Render detail mode after pressing `Enter`.
- [x] Show an empty state when there are no subagent records.
- [x] Truncate/wrap output so rendered lines stay within terminal width.

### Tree navigation

- [x] `↑` selects previous visible node.
- [x] `↓` selects next visible node.
- [x] `←` selects parent node.
- [x] `→` selects first child node.
- [x] `Home` selects first visible node.
- [x] `End` selects last visible node.
- [x] `Enter` opens selected subagent detail.
- [x] `Esc` closes viewer in tree mode.
- [x] `q` closes viewer.

### Detail navigation

- [x] `↑` scrolls detail up.
- [x] `↓` scrolls detail down.
- [x] `PageUp` scrolls detail up by page.
- [x] `PageDown` scrolls detail down by page.
- [x] `Home` jumps to detail top.
- [x] `End` jumps to detail bottom.
- [x] `Esc` returns to tree mode.
- [x] `q` closes viewer.

